Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.56,0:01:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I'll review it one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.56,0:01:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Normally the Eva runs off electricity\Nprovided by an umbilical cable.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.86,0:01:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,In emergencies, it can switch to\Nan internal battery,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.19,0:02:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,with an active life of one minute at full power,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.03,0:02:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,and no more than five minutes in\Nthe minimal activity gain mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.37,0:02:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the limitations of\Nour current technology.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.58,0:02:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.87,0:02:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.87,0:02:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Now let's continue from where we left off\Nyesterday. We'll initiate Induction Mode.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.21,0:02:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Position the target in the center,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.30,0:02:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,then switch "on".
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.30,0:02:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down. Position the target in the center.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.89,0:02:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Switch...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.73,0:02:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Next!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.57,0:02:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm surprised that Shinji\Nagreed to pilot it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.24,0:02:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,He simply does what he's told to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.58,0:02:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe that's his way of getting through life.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.34,0:03:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Target in the center, pull the switch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.92,0:03:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Target in the center, pull the switch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.18,0:03:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Target in the center, pull the switch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.76,0:03:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Target in the center, pull the switch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.31,0:03:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Target in the center...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.73,0:03:17.19,Title Cards,,0,0,0,,{\pos(356.773,431.5)}{\fs75}EPISODE THREE\N{\fs95}THE SILENT PHONE
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.36,0:03:21.86,BG,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And now, from Tokyo we go to\NMiss Natsuko Shinohara in Matsuzaki.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.86,0:03:25.66,BG,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Good morning, this is Shinohara.\NGuess what?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.66,0:03:29.74,BG,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Today I'm in Matsuzaki in West lzu\Nfor a little scuba diving!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.74,0:03:33.00,BG,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Today's forecast is sunny, with an\Nestimated high of 32 degrees C.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.29,0:03:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Misato, it's morning already.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.00,0:03:37.08,BG,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We have hot days all year now,\Nbut we used to have four seasons:{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.83,0:03:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I just got back from night duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.50,0:03:40.38,BG,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Spring, Summer, Fall and Winter.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.75,0:03:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have to go to work until this\Nevening, so please, let me sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.38,0:03:45.30,BG,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We never see snow these days,\Ninstead, due to the recent warmth,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.05,0:03:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.30,0:03:46.80,BG,,0,0,0,,{\i1}aquatic life has been coming back\Nlittle by little.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.30,0:03:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, is today Thursday?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.80,0:03:51.10,BG,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As you dive into the sea you can\Nclearly see an abundance of fish.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.34,0:03:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Take the burnable trash\Nto the garbage, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.68,0:03:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.64,0:03:59.23,BG,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It makes me think of catching some\Nfor tonight's dinner.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.35,0:03:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,So, are you adjusting to school?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.60,0:03:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.06,0:03:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay. See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.23,0:04:02.07,BG,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Although the town brings back sad\Nmemories, this is a hot diving spot.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.86,0:04:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.04,0:04:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes? Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.63,0:04:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's you, Ritsuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.84,0:04:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,How's it going? Are you getting along\Nwith your boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.51,0:04:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.09,0:04:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you mean Shinji.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.13,0:04:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, he transferred into school two\Nweeks ago and he hasn't changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.89,0:04:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No one ever calls him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.76,0:04:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Calls him?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.02,0:04:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, since I figured he'd need one,\NI gave him a cell phone a while back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.19,0:04:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think he's ever used it though,\Nor received any calls.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.65,0:04:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure, but I don't think\Nhe has any friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.32,0:04:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I would guess that Shinji's not\Nthe sort who makes friends easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.70,0:04:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know the fable of the\N"Hedgehog's Dilemma"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.66,0:04:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hedgehog? You mean those animals\Nwith the spiny hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.62,0:05:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though a hedgehog may wish\Nto get close to another hedgehog,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.54,0:05:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,the closer they get, the more they\Ninjure each other with their spines.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.05,0:05:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the same with some humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.43,0:05:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji is probably afraid of pain and has\Nbecome a coward somewhere in his heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.97,0:05:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, he'll eventually learn that growing up
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.39,0:05:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,means getting closer to people\Nand distancing them,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.02,0:05:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,finding a distance where you can avoid\Nhurting each other too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.91,0:05:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up, class rep?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.37,0:05:45.04,Sloppy Sign,,0,0,0,,{\frz4.729\pos(556.955,495.5)}Class Daybook
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.67,0:05:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you give him the printout\NI gave you yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.96,0:05:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.13,0:05:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, there wasn't anybody home\Nat Toji's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.38,0:05:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Aida, you're good friends\Nwith Suzuhara, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.34,0:05:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,He's been absent for two weeks.\NAren't you worried?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.31,0:05:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you suppose he's been seriously injured?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.97,0:06:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What? In that robot incident?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.52,0:06:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The television report said\Nthat nobody was injured!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.44,0:06:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,No way, you saw the explosion site\Non Mount Takanosu, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.23,0:06:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only were Iruma and\NKomatsu dispatched,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.65,0:06:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,they brought in troops from\NMisawa and Kyushu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.53,0:06:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,There had to have been well over\Na couple dozen people injured,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.78,0:06:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and even some killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.74,0:06:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Toji!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.95,0:06:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Suzuhara!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.29,0:06:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, has the class population\Ndropped or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.46,0:06:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,They've all evacuated and\Ntransferred to other schools.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.30,0:06:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, no one wants to stay after\Nthat fierce battle inside the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.38,0:06:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're probably the only one
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.09,0:06:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,who's actually enjoyin' the chance\Nto see a real war.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.14,0:06:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose so.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.31,0:06:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So where have you been, Toji?\NYou were gone for so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.31,0:06:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you get caught in the crossfire\Nor something?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.02,0:06:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,My kid sister did.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.19,0:06:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,She was crushed under a pile of debris.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.86,0:06:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,She survived, but she's been\Nin the hospital ever since.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.70,0:06:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Both my pop and gramps work at the lab,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.49,0:07:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,and there's no way they can\Nleave their posts right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.33,0:07:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So, if I ain't with her, she's all alone\Nat the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.08,0:07:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, that robot's pilot was plain awful!\NI'm downright pissed off!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.96,0:07:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell's the point of\Nour own guy wreckin' the city?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.76,0:07:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, about the pilot, have you heard the\Nrumor about the new transfer student?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.47,0:07:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Transfer student?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.26,0:07:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Him, over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.68,0:07:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,He transferred here while you were absent.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.56,0:07:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,He came right after the incident.\NDon't you think that's odd?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.11,0:07:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,All rise!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.99,0:07:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, humankind was about to face\Nits greatest trial.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.37,0:07:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,In the last year of the 20th century,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.66,0:07:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,the massive meteor from space slammed\Ninto the continent of Antarctica.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.54,0:07:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The continent's ice cap was melted\Nalmost instantaneously.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.55,0:07:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The water level of the oceans rose,\Nthe Earth was thrown off its axis,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.88,0:08:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and abnormal weather patterns threatened\Nthe lives of all living things.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.18,0:08:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Several thousand species and half of the\Nworld's population were lost for eternity.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.23,0:08:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the so-called "Second lmpact".
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.36,0:08:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The survivors still had to live through the hell
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.70,0:08:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,of worldwide economic collapse,\Nethnic conflicts, and civil wars.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.01,0:08:22.81,Fancy Signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,140)}Is it true that you’re the pilot of that robot? Y/N
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.99,0:08:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,However, it has been fifteen years since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.66,0:08:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,In only fifteen years,\Nwe have restored ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.71,0:08:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,This is certainly proof of the human race's\Nresilience, but even more so,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.15,0:08:31.74,Fancy Signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(904.773,236.25)}It’s true, isn’t it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.71,0:08:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,it is the fruit of the blood, sweat and tears
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.88,0:08:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,your fathers and mothers have\Ndedicated to this cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.68,0:08:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.93,0:08:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?! Oh, wow! Cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.77,0:08:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I lived in Nebukawa at the time,\Nwhich is underwater now...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.93,0:08:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, the new student was?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.65,0:08:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.85,0:08:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We're still in class, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.27,0:08:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Sit down now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.52,0:08:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, you're always so bossy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.57,0:08:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay, it's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.40,0:08:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not okay!\NIt's okay, it's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.86,0:08:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.82,0:08:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.74,0:09:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, how were you chosen?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.87,0:09:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Were there any tests?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.45,0:09:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Weren't you scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.49,0:09:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the cockpit look like?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.37,0:09:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's all secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.00,0:09:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's the name of the robot?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.46,0:09:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know much, but everyone\Ncalls it Eva or Unit 01.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.88,0:09:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Eva?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.80,0:09:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And what's its ultimate attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.97,0:09:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Some kind of knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.80,0:09:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It vibrates... An ultra-sonic wave...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.06,0:09:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That's amazing! You're the pride\Nof the school!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.81,0:09:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right! Cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.14,0:09:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And thus...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.81,0:09:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.36,0:09:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.28,0:09:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Ikari, where do you live?\NAll rise! Bow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.66,0:09:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you guys, why don't you at least\Nshow some manners at the end?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.29,0:09:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, transfer student,\Nbut I've gotta beat you up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.55,0:09:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't feel right until I've smacked you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.88,0:10:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, his little sister was injured\Nin the incident the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.97,0:10:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, there you have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.68,0:10:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not piloting it by choice either.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.26,0:10:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,An emergency call.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.22,0:10:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.27,0:10:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,A special state of emergency\Nhas been declared
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.86,0:11:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,for the Kanto and Chubu regions\Nsurrounding the Tokai district.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.90,0:11:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,All residents must evacuate to their\Ndesignated shelters immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.53,0:11:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Repeating...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.09,0:11:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The target has been sighted by our cameras.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.63,0:11:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's already penetrated into\Nour territorial waters.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.30,0:11:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,All personnel, assume\Nbattle stations, Level One.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.72,0:11:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger, prepare for anti-aircraft interception.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.51,0:11:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,New Tokyo-3 transforming\Nto battle formation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.64,0:11:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Initiate accommodation of the central block.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.72,0:12:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Accommodation of central block
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.26,0:12:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and the first through seventh districts\Nhas been completed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.22,0:12:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Notification of the government and other\Nrelated ministries, completed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.68,0:12:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Target is still advancing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.31,0:12:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Present operational rate of anti-aircraft\Ninterception: 48%.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.90,0:12:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the status of noncombatants\Nand civilians?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.40,0:12:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We've already received reports that\Nthe evacuation has been completed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.32,0:12:26.36,Fancy Signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(988,60)}{\fs42}Underground Shelter 334\NDisaster Prevention Department, Tokyo-3
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.32,0:12:26.36,Fancy Signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(724.409,877.25)}Total Floor Space
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.32,0:12:26.36,Fancy Signs,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1171.773,877.25)}Maximum Capacity
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.36,0:12:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Attention, elementary school and\Njunior high school students.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.20,0:12:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Please form groups with\Nyour individual classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.03,0:12:33.74,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\i1\pos(960,225)\fs45}At noon today, a special emergency declaration was issued for the Kanto and Central regions centering on the Tokai area.\NDetails will be reported as they come in.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.41,0:12:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Not again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.91,0:12:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Just text messages again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.37,0:12:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's news censorship. They won't\Nshow any of it to us civilians.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.04,0:12:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though it's an incredible event.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.05,0:12:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The fourth Angel would show up\Nwhile Commander lkari is away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.47,0:12:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a lot sooner than we expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.10,0:12:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The last time they gave us\Na fifteen year break.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.35,0:12:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,This time it's been only three weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.81,0:12:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,They never care about\Nour convenience, do they?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.19,0:13:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,They're the type we women hate the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.40,0:13:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a waste of the taxpayers' money.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.91,0:13:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The committee is demanding that\Nwe dispatch an Evangelion again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.62,0:13:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Those pesky bastards.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.45,0:13:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if they hadn't asked for it,\NI'd have dispatched it anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.92,0:13:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Entry procedure initiated.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.34,0:13:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,LCL oxygenated.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.80,0:13:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Releasing airlock.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.76,0:13:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Why am I piloting this thing again,\Neven though my father's not here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.43,0:13:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though I got beat up?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.15,0:13:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I need to talk to you,\Nprivately, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.65,0:13:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What for?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.52,0:13:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Just give me a second, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.49,0:13:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.70,0:13:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Class rep!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.41,0:13:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.16,0:13:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We both hafta go to the john!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.45,0:13:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You were supposed to use the bathroom\Nbefore you came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.83,0:13:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what's this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.58,0:14:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got to see it, at least once in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.38,0:14:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean the battle up there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.75,0:14:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody knows when the enemy\Nwill come the next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.25,0:14:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Kensuke, are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.59,0:14:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,If we let this opportunity escape us,\Nwe may lose it forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.26,0:14:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, help me unlock the gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.22,0:14:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But you'll get killed if you go out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.89,0:14:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know if that'll happen,\Neven if we stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.81,0:14:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,If I could be killed anyway,\NI'd rather see it first.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.02,0:14:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot. What do you think Nerv's for?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.31,0:14:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And what is Nerv's most important weapon?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.15,0:14:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the robot the new kid pilots.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.53,0:14:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,He protected us the other day,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.86,0:14:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,but you hit him pretty hard. Twice!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.87,0:14:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,If he refuses to pilot the robot,\Nwe're all going to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.16,0:14:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you have a duty to watch him fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.71,0:14:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.67,0:14:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure are upfront about what you want,\Nain't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.30,0:14:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji, are you ready to head out?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.14,0:14:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.89,0:15:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen to me. Neutralize the enemy's AT field,\Nthen fire a volley from the pallet gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.85,0:15:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it just like we practiced.\NCan you handle that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.85,0:15:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.98,0:15:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Launch!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.83,0:15:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Cool! All my efforts really paid off!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.38,0:15:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! This is what I've been waiting for!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.22,0:15:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.35,0:15:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The AT field has been deployed.\NTarget in the center, pull the switch.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.44,0:15:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it just as planned, okay, Shinji?\NTarget in the center, pull the switch.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.98,0:15:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.82,0:15:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot! You hid the enemy\Nwith your own smoke!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.83,0:16:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell?! He's already losing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.96,0:16:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.96,0:16:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sending you a spare rifle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.30,0:16:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Take it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.51,0:16:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji? Shinji?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.43,0:16:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.26,0:16:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Being beaten up must have\Nreally messed him up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.81,0:16:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.58,0:16:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The umbilical cable's been severed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.33,0:16:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Eva has switched to its internal\Nbattery power source.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.54,0:16:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,4 minutes, 53 seconds\Nof activation remaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.89,0:17:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's comin' this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.89,0:17:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji, are you all right? Shinji!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.77,0:17:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Damage report?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.61,0:17:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,No problems detected. He can make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.79,0:17:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji's classmates?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.79,0:17:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What are they doing there?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.55,0:17:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Why won't he fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.43,0:17:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Because we're here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.68,0:17:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,He can't move because of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.60,0:17:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Unit 01 activation time remaining,\N3 minutes 28 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.56,0:17:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji, let them into the cockpit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.94,0:17:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you've got them,\Nmake a temporary retreat.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.49,0:18:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll regroup!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.53,0:18:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You think you can allow unauthorized\Ncivilians into the entry plug?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.91,0:18:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm authorizing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.37,0:18:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You're exceeding your authority,\NCaptain Katsuragi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.41,0:18:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Unit 01's remaining activation time,\N3 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.38,0:18:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold Eva on your current commands\Nand eject the entry plug. Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.84,0:18:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You two! Get in! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.47,0:18:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What the... It's water?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.56,0:18:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,My camera! My camera!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.14,0:18:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Abnormal conditions occurring\Nin the nervous system!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.31,0:18:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course. It's because you've allowed\Ntwo foreign bodies into the plug.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.77,0:18:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,They're introducing noise\Nin the nerve impulse systems!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.87,0:18:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Now! Retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.41,0:18:55.46,BG,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Recovery route 34, retreat to\Nthe east side of the mountain.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.96,0:18:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, new kid, she said, "Retreat!"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.50,0:18:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I mustn't run away. I mustn't run away.\NNew kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.09,0:19:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I mustn't run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.88,0:19:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Progressive Knife engaged!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.43,0:19:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Obey my orders, Shinji! You've got to retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.60,0:19:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.73,0:19:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.46,0:19:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Unit 01, activation time\Nremaining, 30 seconds!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.04,0:19:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,28... 27...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.30,0:19:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,26... 25...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.22,0:19:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,14... 13...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.06,0:19:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,12... 11...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.85,0:19:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,10... 9...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.93,0:19:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,8... 7...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.73,0:19:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,6... 5...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.48,0:19:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,4...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.40,0:19:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,3...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.27,0:19:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,2...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.98,0:20:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,1...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.49,0:20:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Eva Unit 01, activation ceased.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.62,0:20:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The target is completely silent.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.16,0:20:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.04,0:21:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean, since we were chewed out?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.25,0:21:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,No, since he stopped comin' to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.59,0:21:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's "he"?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.88,0:21:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The new kid, the new kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.76,0:21:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what he's been doin' since then?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.76,0:21:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you worried about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.22,0:21:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not exactly worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.18,0:21:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Toji, for someone who's so tactless,\Nyou're pretty stubborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.60,0:21:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,If you had apologized to him back then,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.77,0:21:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,you wouldn't have had to agonize\Nover it for three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.65,0:21:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, this is the new kid's phone number.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.07,0:21:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're so worried, why don't you call him?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.85,0:22:00.89,Title Cards,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(1043.4,687)}TO BE CONTINUED
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.38,0:23:07.25,Title Cards,,0,0,0,,{\pos(793,23)}PREVIEW
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.75,0:23:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Unable to overcome his feelings,\NShinji even runs away from Misato.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.51,0:23:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But the organization brings him\Nback without hesitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.38,0:23:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,There were no kind words waiting for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.64,0:23:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Next Evangelion:\N"Rain, After Running Away"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.39,0:23:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course, I'll give you lots\Nof fan service next time too!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.68,0:23:21.39,ED Title Cards,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,733)}RAIN, AFTER RUNNING AWAY
